---
title: Southern Style Chicken Chilli with Mash & Chives
description: With punchy flavours, lots of goodness (thanks, steamed veggies!) and a tantalising mix of soft and crisp textures,
this delightful chicken chilli is an ode to nostalgic winter nights filled with Southern-style home cooking.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
